<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Not Found | Green Haven Nursery</title>
    <style>
        /* CSS Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Header Styles */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2e7d32, #1b5e20);
            color: white;
            padding: 1.5rem 0;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            background-color: #388e3c;
            padding: 0.8rem 0;
        }

        nav ul {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            list-style: none;
        }

        nav li {
            margin: 0 1rem;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Error Content */
        .error-container {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .error-icon {
            font-size: 5rem;
            color: #d32f2f;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .error-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #1b5e20;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .error-message {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #555;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #1b5e20;
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #134616;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            color: #1b5e20;
            border: 1px solid #1b5e20;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: #e8f5e9;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: #1b5e20;
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .copyright {
            padding-top: 1.5rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #388e3c;
        }

        /* Responsive Adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .error-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .error-message {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            
            nav ul {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            
            nav li {
                margin: 0.3rem 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">Green Haven Nursery</div>
    </header>
    
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Plants</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Garden Supplies</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">About</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    
    <main class="error-container">
        <div class="error-icon">‚ùå</div>
        <h1 class="error-title">Account Not Found</h1>
        <p class="error-message">
            We couldn't find an account associated with the information you provided. 
            Please check your details and try again, or create a new account if you're new to Green Haven Nursery.
        </p>
        <div class="action-buttons">
            <a href="login.html" class="btn btn-primary">Try Again</a>
            <a href="register.html" class="btn btn-secondary">Create New Account</a>
            <a href="index.html" class="btn btn-secondary">Return Home</a>
        </div>
    </main>
    
    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <p>123 Garden Lane, Greenville, GV 12345</p>
            <p>Phone: (555) 123-4567 | Email: info@greenhavennursery.com</p>
        </div>
        <div class="copyright">
            <p>&copy; 2023 Green Haven Nursery. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>